.vault-init.json

# Docs
CLAUDE.md
*.md

# NOTE: migrations are intentionally NOT excluded.
# sqlx::migrate!("./migrations") is a compile-time macro — it reads and
# embeds the .sql files into the binary during `cargo build`. Excluding
# them from the build context causes a compile error.
# Cache concern: moot — the `touch *.rs` step already forces a full
# recompile on every build regardless of what files changed.
